&lt;li&gt;Negotiate and conclude repayment agreements with customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and submit standardized applications to courts and bailiffs for debt recovery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and share case information and documentation with legal and collection partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to official inquiries from courts, bailiffs, and other authorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accurately document interactions and updates in CRM system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and manage assigned portfolio, ensuring performance and progress&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with applicable laws, regulations, and internal policies&lt;/li&gt;
